{"id":"4ffd0534-bafb-4a20-a982-6ba106c4e000","title":"1557/10: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"217f656a-a352-40a1-9c18-61c31a9d4dfd","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, September ..., 1557.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"717470c3-2bfc-42b2-8a06-d0b5cdc8a3cb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"39625ab7-6913-4b9a-8a09-d8af61331496","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"8c1c1574-257c-4e4d-abd1-d163f9d976ed","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"94a0178c-ce60-4b8b-b12b-82623be0fe50","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"e1cd2d79-f127-4dac-9aac-7245d10d6ad3","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3ed25cab-01c2-45a6-b5cc-fbdbe8c9a461","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"69fbc6a9-a87b-4b5c-a44d-a630bc47564e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5a6bb16a-5278-4442-a57f-69a56c28501a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2def0d00-d6c2-42b2-862f-55c9e88b5e45","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0From thy last letter I learnt of the terrible havoc wrought among the bridges and monasteries and houses, together with the number of people who were drowned in the flood. In comparison with what happened to others I think ye\u00A0were tolerably fortunate. I had already heard about it, so I suppose ye have also heard that we have had a similar disaster here, much damage being done and many persons killed by the flooding of the Tiber. As we are placed on high ground we came off exceeding well in comparison with other people. Pray God no greater harm befall us; which, on account of our\u00A0sins, I fear.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"bf5bae44-d83c-4dfc-a65d-b7a660687b56","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"58b97eab-f331-4f24-bf43-825db5a1c1ae","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"995929ac-e25e-4e0b-a4d5-3224b6489b01","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":17,"end":19,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5bf0139f-0f10-4e0f-9814-58a0ef407a42","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":33,"end":33,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3936dea1-7f74-4143-a378-eec74afc5525","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":82,"end":88,"value":"96dcb277-75b5-4056-80a8-1fb671d916a2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c2e00cbf-2a31-4af4-b6c4-040be474ff84","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":94,"end":104,"value":"44af50fb-6f41-4c05-9956-fd9ccab31be2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"344b3332-f32a-4136-b13c-5d77343191b7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":110,"end":115,"value":"7c083741-2180-4be1-b0d8-b0f717e7dbc3","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8f4d5791-73b9-4fdc-bbd4-bbb933514b3f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":146,"end":151,"value":"daf0c662-dead-477d-a711-e6d6ecac0e32","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"980b6d21-03ff-4308-a5e5-cb976c7a9941","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":153,"end":155,"value":"daf0c662-dead-477d-a711-e6d6ecac0e32","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"47698a0f-80fc-4ebd-a3cd-7d3898a65722","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":177,"end":181,"value":"daa506bb-3766-44e9-81c2-348ffde1de9e","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"63254900-776a-46dd-9b79-34476266360c","type":"codex/claim-reference","start":